#ROOM
Vnum     25000
Name     &OThe Valley of Trials - The Den&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand before a massive, crude structure made of earth and heavy
timber known as The Den. This sunk-in valley is the cradle of the new
Horde, where young orcs and trolls are tested to see if they are worthy
of serving the Warchief.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25001
Desc      The dusty center of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25003 1 25000
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25001
Name     &OThe Valley of Trials - Center&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The red dirt here is baked hard by the relentless sun. Lazy peons sleep
in the shade of the few thorny trees, while young warriors chase after
the tough Mottled Boars that root through the dust.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25002
Desc      The northern edge of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25003
Desc      A rocky gorge.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25000
Desc      The Den.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25000 2 25001
  Reset G 1 25000 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25002
Name     &OThe Valley of Trials - North&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The canyon walls close in tightly here, providing a small bit of shade
from the glaring sun. The boars are more plentiful here, aggressive and
territorial.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25001
Desc      The center of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25004
Desc      A dark cave entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25000 2 25002
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25003
Name     &OThe Valley of Trials - East&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The ground becomes rocky and treacherous. The shadows of the canyon wall
hide deadly Scorpid Workers that scurry out to pinch the boots of unwary
travelers.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25001
Desc      The center of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25007
Desc      A hidden, shaded canyon.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25001 2 25003
  Reset G 1 25001 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25004
Name     &OThe Burning Blade Coven - Entrance&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A dark, ominous cave mouth cuts into the northern canyon wall. The air
smells sharply of ozone and fel magic. Cackling Vile Familiars dance
around the entrance, hurling small sparks of green fire.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25002
Desc      The northern valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    25005
Desc      Descend into the coven.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25002 2 25004
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25005
Name     &dThe Burning Blade Coven - Depths&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The air in the cave is suffocatingly hot. The walls glow with a faint,
sickly green light. Cultists have set up a crude altar here, summoning
minor demons to test their dark magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    25004
Desc      The cave entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25006
Desc      Deeper into the twisting tunnels.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25002 2 25005
  Reset G 1 25003 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25006
Name     &dThe Burning Blade Coven - The Altar&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     A large, flat rock serves as an altar for the Burning Blade. Blood and
fel soot stain the stone. The familiars here are numerous and highly
aggressive, swarming anyone who approaches.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25005
Desc      The upper cave.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25002 3 25006
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25007
Name     &OSarkoth's Lair&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A small, dead-end canyon littered with the bones of boars and careless
peons. Sarkoth, a massive and unusually vicious scorpid, claims this
shaded patch of dirt as his own.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25003
Desc      The eastern valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25004 1 25007
  Reset E 1 25004 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25008
Name     &OPath Out of the Valley&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A narrow, winding path leads out of the Valley of Trials and into the
greater expanse of Durotar. The wind picks up, carrying the salty scent
of the ocean from the southeast.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25000
Desc      The Den.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25009
Desc      The outskirts of a troll village.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25009
Name     &OSen'jin Village - Outskirts&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The red dirt begins to mix with white beach sand. You approach a coastal
settlement built by the Darkspear trolls. Crude wooden totems and fishing
nets line the path.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25008
Desc      The path back to the Valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25010
Desc      The center of Sen'jin Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25015
Desc      The Durotar coastline.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25010
Name     &OSen'jin Village - Center&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A bustling, peaceful village of island trolls. They have found a new home
here on the coast, fiercely loyal to the orcs who saved them. Sen'jin
Watchers stand guard, keeping an eye on the treacherous islands just
offshore.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25009
Desc      The village outskirts.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25011
Desc      The beach.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25007 2 25010
Reset O 0 25008 2 25010
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25011
Name     &CThe Coastal Beach&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The warm waters of the Great Sea lap gently against the white sand. To
the east, across a shallow strait of water, you can see the dense, jungle-
like foliage of the Echo Isles.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25010
Desc      Sen'jin Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25012
Desc      Wade into the shallows.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25012
Name     &CThe Echo Isles - Shallows&d~
Sector   water_noswim~
Desc     You wade through the warm, waist-deep water separating the mainland from
the Echo Isles. The trolls of Sen'jin warn that the islands are cursed,
taken over by dark voodoo.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25011
Desc      The mainland beach.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25013
Desc      The shores of the Echo Isles.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25013
Name     &GThe Echo Isles - Shore&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The moment you step onto the island, the atmosphere changes. The trees
are unnaturally thick, and the sound of chanting echoes through the brush.
Echo Isle Hexxers patrol the beaches, hurling curses at intruders.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25012
Desc      The shallow water.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25014
Desc      The heart of the island.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25008 2 25013
  Reset E 1 25009 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25014
Name     &GZalazane's Fall&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The center of the Echo Isles is completely corrupted by dark magic. A
massive, bubbling cauldron of voodoo brews in the center of the clearing.
The mad witch doctor Zalazane dances wildly around it, commanding his
enthralled brethren.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25013
Desc      The island shore.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25009 1 25014
  Reset G 1 25010 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25015
Name     &OThe Durotar Coastline&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Heading north from Sen'jin Village, the coastline becomes rugged and
rocky. Shipwrecks litter the shore. In the distance, a large, stone
fortress flies the green and gold anchor flag of Kul Tiras.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25009
Desc      Sen'jin Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25016
Desc      The approach to the keep.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25019
Desc      The central plains of Durotar.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25016
Name     &OTiragarde Keep - Approach&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The path winds up a steep hill toward the human fortress. The Kul Tiras
Marines have dug in deep here, determined to wipe out the Horde before
it can establish a foothold in Kalimdor.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25015
Desc      The coastline.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25017
Desc      The courtyard of the keep.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25005 2 25016
