#ROOM
Vnum     25018
Name     &OTiragarde Keep - The Tower&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The command center of the Kul Tiras invasion. Lieutenant Benedict stands
over a map table, plotting the destruction of Orgrimmar. He is a seasoned
veteran, incredibly tough and utterly ruthless.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    25017
Desc      The courtyard below.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25006 1 25018
  Reset G 1 25007 10
