#ROOM
Vnum     25019
Name     &OThe Central Plains&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The harsh, red plains of Durotar stretch out in all directions. The heat
is oppressive. Sleek, deadly Durotar Tigers use the tall, dry grass to
stalk their prey, striking with lightning speed.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25015
Desc      The coastline.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25020
Desc      A major crossroads.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25010 2 25019
  Reset E 1 25011 10 3
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25020
Name     &OThe Crossroads to Razor Hill&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The dirt path widens into a major, heavily traveled road. Peons carry
lumber and stone along this route. To the north, the imposing wooden
watchtowers of Razor Hill rise above the canyon walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25019
Desc      The central plains.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25021
Desc      The gates of Razor Hill.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25025
Desc      A rocky path leading east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25021
Name     &ORazor Hill - South Gate&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Massive logs have been sharpened and lashed together to form the walls
of Razor Hill. It is the primary military outpost for the Horde in Durotar,
heavily guarded by seasoned orc grunts.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25020
Desc      The crossroads.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25022
Desc      The center of the outpost.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25011 2 25021
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25022
Name     &ORazor Hill - Center&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A bustling hub of activity. Merchants sell their wares, warriors rest
between patrols, and peons are constantly yelled at to work harder. An
inn provides a safe resting place for weary travelers.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25021
Desc      The south gate.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25023
Desc      The barracks.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25024
Desc      The northern watchtower.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25028
Desc      The path to Orgrimmar.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25011 1 25022
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25023
Name     &ORazor Hill - Barracks&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The military command center for the region. Weapons line the walls, and
maps of Kul Tiras and centaur movements are scattered on tables. Commander
Gar'thok coordinates the defense of Durotar from here.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25022
Desc      The center of Razor Hill.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25012 1 25023
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25024
Name     &ORazor Hill - Northern Watchtower&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A tall wooden tower providing a commanding view of the northern canyons.
From here, guards can see all the way to the massive iron gates of the
capital city, Orgrimmar.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25022
Desc      The center of Razor Hill.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25025
Name     &OPath to Skull Rock&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     This rocky path winds east from the main road, leading into the jagged
cliffs bordering the sea. The air grows cold, and an unsettling silence
falls over the canyon.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25020
Desc      The crossroads.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25026
Desc      The entrance to Skull Rock.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25026
Name     &OSkull Rock - Entrance&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A massive cave opening naturally shaped like a terrifying, screaming
skull. This is the hidden base of the Burning Blade cult in Durotar.
Fel magic oozes from the stone itself.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25025
Desc      The path back to the road.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25027
Desc      Enter the dark cavern.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25013 2 25026
  Reset E 1 25012 10 5
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25027
Name     &dSkull Rock - Depths&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The caverns are vast and labyrinthine. Burning Blade Cultists perform
unspeakable rituals in the dark, summoning demons and plotting the
downfall of the Warchief. The warlock Gazz'uz oversees the corruption.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25026
Desc      The cave entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25013 2 25027
Reset M 0 25014 1 25027
  Reset G 1 25013 10
