#ROOM
Vnum     25028
Name     &OThe Dustwind Gulch&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     Leaving Razor Hill to the west, the canyon narrows significantly. The
wind howls through the gulch, kicking up blinding clouds of red dust.
The massive, spiked iron walls of Orgrimmar are visible just ahead.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25022
Desc      Razor Hill.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25029
Desc      The Gates of Orgrimmar.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25029
Name     &OThe Gates of Orgrimmar&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand before the awe-inspiring, impregnable iron gates of the Horde
capital. The sheer scale of the architecture is breathtaking. Massive
bonfires burn on either side of the entrance, and elite Kor'kron guards
stand watch. Your journey into the heart of the Horde begins here.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25028
Desc      The Dustwind Gulch back to Razor Hill.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11200
Desc      Enter the Valley of Strength.
~
